translate french danas4_2d652afd:

    # cw "Hrm, I don't know."
    cw "Hum, je ne sais pas."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danas4.rpy:18
translate french danas4_c2d3d95b:

    # cw "I don't really watch a lot of movies anymore."
    cw "Je ne regarde plus vraiment beaucoup de films."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danas4.rpy:20
translate french danas4_9199cd9d:

    # cw "I used to go to the movies all the time, but now I'm always so busy with work and taking care of the housework at home, I just never have the time."
    cw "Avant, j’allais tout le temps au cinéma, mais maintenant je suis toujours tellement occupée par le travail et les tâches ménagères à la maison que je n’ai tout simplement plus le temps."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danas4.rpy:22
translate french danas4_92bbff8e:

    # cw "Plus Terry doesn't really like going to the movies."
    cw "En plus, Terry n’aime pas vraiment aller au cinéma."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danas4.rpy:24
translate french danas4_6c61963e:

    # cw "Back in college though, I really liked watching horror movies in the theater."
    cw "À l’époque de la fac, par contre, j’aimais beaucoup aller voir des films d’horreur au cinéma."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danas4.rpy:26
translate french danas4_439df047:

    # cw "Although to be honest, I didn't watch a lot of the movie on those dates, if you know what I mean."
    cw "Même si, pour être honnête, je ne regardais pas grand-chose du film pendant ces rendez-vous, si tu vois ce que je veux dire."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danas4.rpy:27
translate french danas4_fa76fc71:

    # pc "I think I do."
    pc "Je crois que oui."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danas4.rpy:28
translate french danas4_3dddc7e8:

    # cw "I thought you might."
    cw "Je m’en doutais."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danas4.rpy:29
translate french danas4_df0a9fa4:

    # cw "Was fun times though. I'd love to go to the theater again."
    cw "C’était des bons moments, par contre. J’adorerais retourner au cinéma."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danas4.rpy:30
translate french danas4_6f4d5303:

    # pc "Then you should."
    pc "Alors tu devrais."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danas4.rpy:31
translate french danas4_12f7b381:

    # cw "Maybe I will sometime."
    cw "Peut-être que je le ferai un jour."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danas4.rpy:32
translate french danas4_18453400:

    # cw "If I can find somebody to go with me."
    cw "Si je trouve quelqu’un pour m’accompagner."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danas4.rpy:34
translate french danas4_433a35a7:

    # cw "Maybe Liz will go."
    cw "Peut-être que Liz viendra."

